  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST BURNING SKIES</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Test your reflexes in POLYGONEER, defend yourself from prolygonal shapes taht comes from everywhere, just hitting is not enough you need to match the right color shot to the polygon too! Are you ready for the challenge? </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/85d0887d42ac5a3a937104b3345e7896.poster.avif?t=1762263180\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/85d0887d42ac5a3a937104b3345e7896.webm?t=1762263180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/85d0887d42ac5a3a937104b3345e7896.mp4?t=1762263180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Perfect to play when you want to test or improve your reflexes, or while you are on a queue for another game, this is a small and replayable game. The objectives are to beat the 5 stages, get on top of the leaderboards, unlock achievements and beat personal scores and times. </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/d9654fc079750d98bf8b652c274cb3b7.poster.avif?t=1762263180\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/d9654fc079750d98bf8b652c274cb3b7.webm?t=1762263180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/d9654fc079750d98bf8b652c274cb3b7.mp4?t=1762263180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Test your reflex destroying the enemies using the right color shot in one of the 5 levels (or in the hidden HELL level if you're brave enough)<br></li><li>Get bigger scores by not missing any shot, the multiplier increase for every 5 enemies destroyed. If you miss the color or the shot the multiplier return to zero.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/d5d091fb90d8033cf1f3c4770871bd36.poster.avif?t=1762263180\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/d5d091fb90d8033cf1f3c4770871bd36.webm?t=1762263180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/d5d091fb90d8033cf1f3c4770871bd36.mp4?t=1762263180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast paced arcade gameplay.<br></li><li>5 different stages and a hidden hell stage.<br></li><li>Leaderboards for each stage.<br></li><li>Polygonal graphics.<br></li><li>Great to play both with joystick or keyboard.<br></li><li>6 Amazing electro-hardcore original tracks.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Test your reflexes in POLYGONEER, defend yourself from prolygonal shapes taht comes from everywhere, just hitting is not enough you need to match the right color shot to the polygon too! Are you ready for the challenge? </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/85d0887d42ac5a3a937104b3345e7896.poster.avif?t=1762263180\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/85d0887d42ac5a3a937104b3345e7896.webm?t=1762263180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/85d0887d42ac5a3a937104b3345e7896.mp4?t=1762263180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Perfect to play when you want to test or improve your reflexes, or while you are on a queue for another game, this is a small and replayable game. The objectives are to beat the 5 stages, get on top of the leaderboards, unlock achievements and beat personal scores and times. </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/d9654fc079750d98bf8b652c274cb3b7.poster.avif?t=1762263180\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/d9654fc079750d98bf8b652c274cb3b7.webm?t=1762263180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/d9654fc079750d98bf8b652c274cb3b7.mp4?t=1762263180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Test your reflex destroying the enemies using the right color shot in one of the 5 levels (or in the hidden HELL level if you're brave enough)<br></li><li>Get bigger scores by not missing any shot, the multiplier increase for every 5 enemies destroyed. If you miss the color or the shot the multiplier return to zero.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/d5d091fb90d8033cf1f3c4770871bd36.poster.avif?t=1762263180\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/d5d091fb90d8033cf1f3c4770871bd36.webm?t=1762263180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/d5d091fb90d8033cf1f3c4770871bd36.mp4?t=1762263180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast paced arcade gameplay.<br></li><li>5 different stages and a hidden hell stage.<br></li><li>Leaderboards for each stage.<br></li><li>Polygonal graphics.<br></li><li>Great to play both with joystick or keyboard.<br></li><li>6 Amazing electro-hardcore original tracks.</li></ul>",
